{"tid":2331673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美洲鬣蜥｜綠鬣蜥、紅鬣蜥可長至1.5米 坐BB車外出散步、主人混身抓傷：就算被牠虐待都開心","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T12:19:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b072513202143c0de95ce2e418c0569e1aa81921","tid":2331673,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"Bella於三年前開始飼養紅鬣蜥BB及綠鬣蜥檸檬，「喜歡牠的樣子威猛、有型、好像哥斯拉，特別是公的臉有兩塊肉更加有型。有些人看見會覺得很害怕，但帶牠外出時大多數人都覺得很趣緻，原來也有很多人喜歡牠們。」Bella每逢放假日子遇上好太陽，就會帶不怕陌生人的BB外出散步、曬太陽。BB現時已屬成體，由頭至尾總長1.5米，體重13磅，因此要用嬰兒車載着BB外出。另外，為怕BB會突然受驚奔走，故必須為牠戴上爬蟲用牽繩。Bella自BB小時候開始抱牠，讓牠習慣主人的氣味和相處，現時BB不單溫馴，每晚更要跟Bella一起睡覺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201219/XYKBUNMS2NFATEB3RAF3HB3UL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201219%2FXYKBUNMS2NFATEB3RAF3HB3UL4%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=fa4917ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201219%2FXYKBUNMS2NFATEB3RAF3HB3UL4%2F&h=129fc9a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201219/XYKBUNMS2NFATEB3RAF3HB3UL4/</a>"},{"pid":"f2c222dada96e236f4ea700c87c7f2bc0c0d89ce","tid":2331673,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6XowXK1YRzeuu_PoZ5YgPh0ZNPo=/6000x4000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WV6OSPCKKFFTFHU5JBAIIK5AJA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6XowXK1YRzeuu_PoZ5YgPh0ZNPo%3D%2F6000x4000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWV6OSPCKKFFTFHU5JBAIIK5AJA.JPG&h=6db04ff7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0139029e4c15fe184d9c9003d64117f47246dd4","tid":2331673,"uid":21896,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:59:56.000Z","msg":"好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f276c95f076f9638644d0a099471edf21787ff29","tid":2331673,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"狗仔咁"},{"pid":"18ce9724b49207d8f71234e041ccf45b4b7685fb","tid":2331673,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81329ad7c0261afa23c2d7fc6044bb627ae39fbb","tid":2331673,"uid":6297,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"養條恐龍又幾過癮"},{"pid":"d7b4c09933b69a7da9e38439c4fec637cbbb07e1","tid":2331673,"uid":191300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81329ad7c0261afa23c2d7fc6044bb627ae39fbb","tid":2331673,"uid":6297,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"養條恐龍又幾過癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"想養霸王龍&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"8ade77b48c351fcd58f90377b1fad69352310999","tid":2331673,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc12fb311c7488ff9a4d9d5371944fe6608da54c","tid":2331673,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"享和珍禽異獸醫療中心註冊獸醫黃惠淳指，飼養紅或綠鬣蜥最重要注意環境溫度，大約要有攝氏26至35度。「對於爬蟲類來說，曬太陽也非常重要。因為牠們曬太陽之後身體會產生維他命D，維他命D會幫助牠們吸收吃進去的鈣質。所以如果只吃鈣但沒有曬太陽，這樣是沒有用的，鈣質只會直接隨着便便排出來。」另外，常見病有缺鈣、腎衰竭、皮膚霉菌感染及腸道寄生蟲，但倘若環境、食物等等處理妥當，成年鬣蜥也算比較少生病。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7Lkb6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7Lkb6P.jpg&h=68813cf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid